<p>What I have is:</p>  <pre><code>from lxml import etree myscript = "if(0 &lt; 1){alert(\"Hello World!\");}" html = etree.fromstring("&lt;script&gt;&lt;/script&gt;")  for element in html.findall('//script'):     element.text = myscript  result = etree.tostring(html) </code></pre>  <p>What I get is:</p>  <pre><code>&gt;&gt;&gt; result '&lt;script&gt;if(0 &amp;lt; 1){alert("Hello World!");}&lt;/script&gt;' </code></pre>  <p>What I want is <strong>unescaped</strong>  JavaScript:</p>  <pre><code>&gt;&gt;&gt; result '&lt;script&gt;if(0 &lt; 1){alert("Hello World!");}&lt;/script&gt;' </code></pre>